snippet.title: ITHU NIJAM Full Movie | Angel Pictures | Latest Christian Tamil Movie
snippet.description:
#AngelPictures #IthuNijam #TamilChristianMovie

ITHU NIJAM is a 2017 Tamil epic disaster film directed by M. Kumar and Jessy Subash, and stars Vijaykumar, Seetha, Senthil, Vadivukkarasi, Thalaivasal Vijay, Mottai Rajendran, Vincent Asokan and Sundar Selvaraj. The film was produced by Angel Pictures. Filming began in Chengalpatt District in Tamil Nadu in early 2016.

Adaikalapatti, is a village in South India known for its beautiful landscape. Its people lead a peaceful and idyllic life. In such a situation, a series of natural disasters of apocalyptic proportions hit the village disrupting their quiet and peaceful life.

The people in the village are astounded in a state of uncertainty not knowing what to make of it. Scientists are frantic to find answers to these disasters. The plot follows the village's Siddha medicine doctor, Vaithiyalingam, as he attempts to help the villagers to safety amid a worldwide strange happenings of the scientifically unexplained kind.

Adaikalapatti, is continually hit by cataclysmic events. Does this mean an apocalyptic end is approaching? Can their faith save them? Did this village escape from the onslaught of natural disasters? What is the reason behind for the increased natural disasters of apocalyptic proportions all over the world?
